                <div style="padding:15px;">
                    <strong>Q.</strong> Is there a membership fee for this program?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> There is NO membership fee for the Diesel Cult.<br><br>
                    <strong>Q.</strong> How long is membership valid?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> Membership is valid for three years from the date of enrolment. To know more about your membership, log in to the Cult App or check at your nearest Diesel Store.<br><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> What is the procedure for acquiring the exclusive benefits and privileges against my membership?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong>  Below are the procedure for acquiring the benefits and privileges.
                    <li>For redemption of Style Miles on special Cult merchandise, simply log on to your Diesel Cult app.</li>
                    <li>You can visit our store and just tell them your registered mobile number or Cult ID for any kind of special assistance at the store.</li>
                    <li>You can call in to book an appointment with your stylist or personal shopper a day in advance. You can request the blocking of a trial room at least two hours before your arrival.</li>
                    <li>Bookings for the VIP room at Juhu and After hours Shopping can be requested for 24 hours in advance.</li>
                    <li>The booking will be for the appointment day only. It will become null and void the next day.</li>
                    <li>To make all your exclusive bookings and appointments, please call the respective store numbers.</li>
                    <li>Alternatively, a mail can be dropped at <a href="mailto:customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com">customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com</a> with your request.</li><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> From when will the Style Miles get calculated?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> The Style Miles are calculated from the day you become a Classic or Higher Cult member.<br><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> Can I exchange/return any Diesel merchandise which I have bought with my style miles?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> No. The merchandise redeemed against Style Miles cannot be exchanged or returned.<br><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> Can I redeem my Style Miles for cash?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> No. Style Miles cannot be redeemed for cash. They can only be redeemed for Diesel merchandise from the Cult Catalogue.<br><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> How can I check my current style miles?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> The Style Miles can be checked:

                    <li>On your Diesel Cult app</li>
                    <li>At the store: Just provide your Cult ID or the registered mobile number and get your Style Miles statement</li>
                    <li>Email: You can also email us at <a href="mailto:customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com">customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com</a></li><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> How soon will style miles get updated to my account?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> The Style Miles get updated to your account within 48 hours of your last purchase.<br><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> How can I communicate and change in my address or phone number?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> You can update the same in the ‘My Profile’ section of the Diesel Cult app or email us at <a href="mailto:customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com">customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com</a><br><br>

                    <strong>Q.</strong> How can I get in touch with customer care for more queries regarding my membership?<br>
                    <strong>A.</strong> You can email us at <a href="mailto:customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com">customercare_dieselindia@diesel.com</a>. Our Cult executive will call you back for assistance.
